           BLOCK CONTAINS 0 RECORDS                                             
           LABEL RECORDS ARE OMITTED                                            
           DATA RECORD IS PERM-MARK1-SKU-REC.                                   
       01  PERM-MARK1-SKU-REC          PIC X(351).                              
                                                                                
       FD  REP-DATE-INFILE                                                      
           RECORDING MODE F                                                     
