               05  PV-REP-DEPT.                                                 
                   10  PV-REP-DEPT-NBR   PIC  9(03)  VALUE ZERO.                
                   10  FILLER            PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.                 
                   10  PV-REP-DEPT-NM    PIC  X(20)  VALUE SPACES.              
               05  FILLER                PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.              
               05  PV-REP-SUB-CL-NBR     PIC  9(02)  VALUE ZERO.                
