               05  PV-REP-EXPT-DT-NUM    PIC  9(08)  VALUE ZEROES.              
                                                                                
      *****************************************************************         
      *  General workarea sql abend                                    *        
      *****************************************************************         
       01  ABEND-CODE                    PIC S9(04) VALUE +0 COMP SYNC.         
           88  ABEND-4013                           VALUE +4013.                
                                                                                
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.                                                      
      *****************************************************************         
      * Description     : Control main processing flow                *         
      *****************************************************************         
       000-MAIN-CONTROL.                                                        
                                                                                
           PERFORM 0500-INITIALISATION.                                         
                                                                                
           PERFORM 1000-MAIN-PROCESS                                            
             UNTIL EOF-MARK1-FILE.                                              
                                                                                
           PERFORM 9000-TERMINATE.                                              
           STOP RUN.                                                            
                                                                                
       0500-INITIALISATION.                                                     
      *****************************************************************         
      * Description     : Initialise fields and working storage       *         
      *****************************************************************         
                                                                                
           MOVE "*0500-INITIALISATION*"  TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME                   
                                                                                
           INITIALIZE                       PV-PROGRAM-VARIABLES                
                                                                                
           OPEN INPUT                       PERM-MARK1-SKU-CE1                  
                INPUT                       REP-DATE-INFILE                     
                OUTPUT                      PERM-RPT-OUTFILE.                   
                                                                                
           PERFORM 0510-READ-DATE-FILE.                                         
                                                                                
           MOVE SPACES                   TO PV-CURRENT-DATE                     
           PERFORM 0520-GET-CURRENT-DTE                                         
           MOVE PV-CURRENT-DATE(1:2)     TO PV-CURR-DT-CCYYMMDD(1:2)            
           MOVE PV-CURRENT-DATE(3:2)     TO PV-CURR-DT-YY                       
                                            PV-CURR-DT-CCYYMMDD(3:2)            
           MOVE PV-CURRENT-DATE(6:2)     TO PV-CURR-DT-MM                       
                                            PV-CURR-DT-CCYYMMDD(5:2)            
           MOVE PV-CURRENT-DATE(9:2)     TO PV-CURR-DT-DD                       
                                            PV-CURR-DT-CCYYMMDD(7:2)            
           COMPUTE PV-CURR-DT-ED = FUNCTION NUMVAL(PV-CURR-DT-YYMMDD)           
           END-COMPUTE.                                                         
                                                                                
           MOVE PV-CURR-DT-30DAYS(1:4)   TO PV-CURR-DT-30-CCYYMMDD(1:4)         
           MOVE PV-CURR-DT-30DAYS(6:2)   TO PV-CURR-DT-30-CCYYMMDD(5:2)         
           MOVE PV-CURR-DT-30DAYS(9:2)   TO PV-CURR-DT-30-CCYYMMDD(7:2)         
                                                                                
           INITIALIZE                       PV-MARK1-FILE                       
                                            PV-REP-MARK1-FILE.                  
           PERFORM 2000-READ-MARK1-SKU-CE1.                                     
                                                                                
      ****************************************************************          
      * GETS THE DATE GAP TO GET Current DATE - 30 DAYS            *            
      ****************************************************************          
       0510-READ-DATE-FILE.                                                     
                                                                                
           READ REP-DATE-INFILE           INTO CC-RUN-DATE-GAP-REC              
           AT END                                                               
              SET EOF-DATE-GAP-FILE     TO TRUE                                 
           END-READ.                                                            
                                                                                
           IF  EOF-DATE-GAP-FILE                                                
           OR  CC-REP-DATE-GAP = SPACES                                         
               MOVE '0510-READ-DATE-FILE'  TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME                 
               MOVE 'READ                       '                               
                                            TO PV-OPERATION-MSG-1               
               MOVE 'INVALID DATE GAP IN CONTROL CARD'                          
                                            TO PV-OPERATION-MSG-2               
               PERFORM 9200-ABEND                                               
           END-IF                                                               
                                                                                
           MOVE CC-REP-DATE-GAP             TO PV-DATE-GAP.                     
                                                                                
       0520-GET-CURRENT-DTE.                                                    
      *****************************************************************         
      * Description     : To get the current date                     *         
      *****************************************************************         
                                                                                
           PERFORM  WITH TEST AFTER                                             
                   UNTIL SQLCODE = +0                                           
                      OR SQLCODE = +100                                         
                      OR PV-RETRY-COUNT > PC-MAXIMUM-RETRY-COUNT                
                                                                                
                                                                                
               EXEC SQL                                                         
                   SELECT  CURRENT DATE                                         
                          ,(CURRENT DATE - :PV-DATE-GAP DAYS)                   
                     INTO :PV-CURRENT-DATE                                      
                         ,:PV-CURR-DT-30DAYS                                    
                     FROM  SYSIBM.SYSDUMMY1                                     
                   WITH UR                                                      
               END-EXEC                                                         
               EVALUATE TRUE                                                    
                   WHEN SQLCODE = ZERO                                          
                       CONTINUE                                                 
                   WHEN SQLCODE = -911                                          
                   WHEN SQLCODE = -913                                          
                        ADD 1                 TO PV-RETRY-COUNT                 
                   WHEN OTHER                                                   
                       MOVE '0520-GET-CURRENT-DTE'                              
                                              TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME              
                       MOVE 'GET CURRENT DATE'                                  
                                              TO PV-DB2-OPER-ATTEMPTED          
                       PERFORM 9999-SQL-ERROR                                   
               END-EVALUATE                                                     
           END-PERFORM.                                                         
                                                                                
           IF  PV-RETRY-COUNT > PC-MAXIMUM-RETRY-COUNT                          
               MOVE '0520-GET-CURRENT-DTE'    TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME              
               MOVE 'GET CURRENT DATE'        TO PV-DB2-OPER-ATTEMPTED          
               PERFORM 9999-SQL-ERROR                                           
           END-IF.                                                              
                                                                                
                                                                                
       1000-MAIN-PROCESS.                                                       
      *****************************************************************         
      * Description     : Main Processing                             *         
      *****************************************************************         
                                                                                
           MOVE "*1000-MAIN-PROCESS      *"   TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME              
                                                                                
           PERFORM 1100-SELECT-TSKSTOO-TPLNSHP                                  
                                                                                
           MOVE ZEROS                         TO TSKST-LAST-RCVD-DATE           
           PERFORM 1200-SELECT-TSKST-CORP-LVL                                   
                                                                                
           MOVE ZEROS                         TO TSKST-LAST-RCVD-DATE           
           PERFORM 1300-SELECT-TSKST-STR-LVL                                    
                                                                                
           PERFORM 1500-VALIDATE-DATES                                          
                                                                                
           INITIALIZE                            PV-MARK1-FILE                  
                                                 PV-REP-MARK1-FILE.             
           PERFORM 2000-READ-MARK1-SKU-CE1.                                     
                                                                                
       1100-SELECT-TSKSTOO-TPLNSHP.                                             
      ******************************************************************        
      * Description : To get PO number, PO Ship date                            
      ******************************************************************        
                                                                                
           MOVE "*1100-SELECT-TSKSTOO-TPLNSHP"                                  
                                            TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME                
           MOVE PV-ITM-NBR                  TO SKSTOO-ITM-NBR                   
           MOVE PV-STORE-NBR                TO SKSTOO-STR-NBR                   
                                                                                
           EXEC SQL                                                             
               SELECT  TOO.PO_NBR                                               
                      ,TP.DONT_SHIP_BEF_DTE                                     
                      ,(TP.DONT_SHIP_BEF_DTE  + 8 DAYS) EXPECT_RECPT_DT         
                 INTO :SKSTOO-PO-NBR                                            
                     ,:PLNSHP-DONT-SHIP-BEF-DTE                                 
                     ,:PV-EXPT-RCT-DT                                           
                 FROM  TSKSTOO  TOO                                             
                      ,TPLNSHP  TP                                              
                WHERE  TOO.ITM_NBR = DEC(:SKSTOO-ITM-NBR,15,0)                  
                  AND  TP.PO_NBR          = TOO.PO_NBR                          
                  AND  TP.VER_STATUS_CDE  = 'A'                                 
                ORDER BY 2 ASC                                                  
                        ,1 ASC                                                  
                FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY                                          
               WITH UR                                                          
           END-EXEC.                                                            
                                                                                
           EVALUATE SQLCODE                                                     
               WHEN +0                                                          
                   MOVE PV-EXPT-RCT-DT(1:4) TO PV-EXPT-DT-FMT(1:4)              
                   MOVE PV-EXPT-RCT-DT(6:2) TO PV-EXPT-DT-FMT(5:2)              
                   MOVE PV-EXPT-RCT-DT(9:2) TO PV-EXPT-DT-FMT(7:2)              
                                                                                
               WHEN +100                                                        
                   MOVE ZEROES              TO SKSTOO-PO-NBR                    
                   MOVE SPACES              TO PV-EXPT-DT-FMT                   
                                               PLNSHP-DONT-SHIP-BEF-DTE         
               WHEN OTHER                                                       
                   MOVE "SELECT FROM TSKSTOO & TPLNSHP"                         
                                              TO PV-DB2-OPER-ATTEMPTED          
                   DISPLAY SPACES                                               
                   DISPLAY "TSKSTOO.ITM_NBR = "  PV-ITM-NBR                     
                   DISPLAY "TSKSTOO.STR_NBR = "  PV-STORE-NBR                   
                   DISPLAY "TPLNSHP.STATUS_CDE = A"                             
                   PERFORM 9999-SQL-ERROR                                       
           END-EVALUATE.                                                        
                                                                                
       1200-SELECT-TSKST-CORP-LVL.                                              
      ******************************************************************        
      * Description : To get RECENT Last received date at CORP LEVEL            
      ******************************************************************        
                                                                                
           MOVE "*1200-SELECT-TSKST-CORP-LVL" TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME              
           MOVE PV-ITM-NBR                    TO TSKST-ITEM-NMBR                
                                                                                
           EXEC SQL                                                             
               SELECT  T.LAST_RCVD_DATE                                         
                      ,T.ONHAND_QTY                                             
                 INTO :TSKST-LAST-RCVD-DATE                                     
                     ,:TSKST-ONHAND-QTY                                         
                 FROM  TSKST    T                                               
                WHERE  T.LOC_NBR = 0                                            
                  AND  T.ITEM_NMBR = DEC(:TSKST-ITEM-NMBR,15,0)                 
               WITH UR                                                          
           END-EXEC.                                                            
                                                                                
           EVALUATE SQLCODE                                                     
               WHEN +0                                                          
                   PERFORM 1400-CONVERT-LAST-RECPT-DT                           
                   MOVE PV-ED-LST-RCVD-DT     TO PV-CRP-LST-RVD-DT              
                   MOVE TSKST-ONHAND-QTY      TO PV-REP-ONHAND-QTY              
                   MOVE ZEROES                TO PV-ED-LST-RCVD-DT              
                                                 PV-CENTURY                     
               WHEN +100                                                        
                   MOVE ZEROS                 TO PV-CRP-LST-RVD-DT              
                   MOVE ZEROS                 TO PV-REP-ONHAND-QTY              
               WHEN OTHER                                                       
                   MOVE "SELECT FROM TSKST "  TO PV-DB2-OPER-ATTEMPTED          
                   DISPLAY SPACES                                               
                   DISPLAY "TSKST.LOC_NBR = 0 "                                 
                   DISPLAY "TSKST.ITM_NBR = "    PV-ITM-NBR                     
                   PERFORM 9999-SQL-ERROR                                       
           END-EVALUATE.                                                        
                                                                                
       1300-SELECT-TSKST-STR-LVL.                                               
      ******************************************************************        
      * Description : To get RECENT Last received date and ON HAND QTY          
      *               at Store level                                            
      ******************************************************************        
                                                                                
           MOVE "*1300-SELECT-TSKST-STR-LVL  "                                  
                                              TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME              
           MOVE PV-ITM-NBR                    TO TSKST-ITEM-NMBR                
           MOVE PV-STORE-NBR                  TO TSKST-LOC-NBR                  
                                                                                
           EXEC SQL                                                             
               SELECT  T.LAST_RCVD_DATE                                         
                 INTO :TSKST-LAST-RCVD-DATE                                     
                 FROM  TSKST    T                                               
                WHERE  T.LOC_NBR   = :TSKST-LOC-NBR                             
                  AND  T.ITEM_NMBR = DEC(:TSKST-ITEM-NMBR,15,0)                 
               WITH UR                                                          
           END-EXEC.                                                            
                                                                                
           EVALUATE SQLCODE                                                     
               WHEN +0                                                          
                   PERFORM 1400-CONVERT-LAST-RECPT-DT                           
                   MOVE PV-ED-LST-RCVD-DT     TO PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT              
                   MOVE ZEROES                TO PV-ED-LST-RCVD-DT              
                                                 PV-CENTURY                     
               WHEN +100                                                        
                   MOVE ZEROES                TO PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT              
                                                 PV-CRP-LST-RVD-DT              
               WHEN OTHER                                                       
                   MOVE "SELECT FROM TSKST "  TO PV-DB2-OPER-ATTEMPTED          
                   DISPLAY SPACES                                               
                   DISPLAY "TSKST.LOC_NBR = "    PV-STORE-NBR                   
                   DISPLAY "TSKST.ITM_NBR = "    PV-ITM-NBR                     
                   PERFORM 9999-SQL-ERROR                                       
           END-EVALUATE.                                                        
                                                                                
       1400-CONVERT-LAST-RECPT-DT.                                              
      ******************************************************************        
      * Description : Convert Last receipt date Format                          
      ******************************************************************        
                                                                                
           MOVE "*1400-CONVERT-LAST-RECPT-DT"                                   
                                            TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME                
                                                                                
           IF  TSKST-LAST-RCVD-DATE <= ZERO                                     
               MOVE ZEROS                   TO PV-ED-LST-RCVD-DT                
           ELSE                                                                 
                                                                                
               IF  TSKST-LAST-RCVD-DATE > PV-CURR-DT-ED                         
                   MOVE 19                  TO PV-CENTURY                       
               ELSE                                                             
                   MOVE 20                  TO PV-CENTURY                       
               END-IF                                                           
                                                                                
               COMPUTE PV-ED-LST-RCVD-DT =  (TSKST-LAST-RCVD-DATE +             
                                           (PV-CENTURY * 1000000))              
               END-COMPUTE                                                      
                                                                                
           END-IF.                                                              
                                                                                
       1500-VALIDATE-DATES.                                                     
      ******************************************************************        
      * Description : Validate Dates                                            
      ******************************************************************        
                                                                                
           MOVE "*1500-VALIDATE-DATES"      TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME                
                                                                                
           MOVE PV-EFF-DTE(1:4)             TO PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-X(1:4)          
           MOVE PV-EFF-DTE(6:2)             TO PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-X(5:2)          
           MOVE PV-EFF-DTE(9:2)             TO PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-X(7:2)          
           MOVE PV-EFF-DTE-PLUS30(1:4)      TO PV-M1-EFF-DTE30-X(1:4)           
           MOVE PV-EFF-DTE-PLUS30(6:2)      TO PV-M1-EFF-DTE30-X(5:2)           
           MOVE PV-EFF-DTE-PLUS30(9:2)      TO PV-M1-EFF-DTE30-X(7:2)           
                                                                                
P11295     PERFORM 7100-GET-MARK1-MIN30DAYS.                                    
                                                                                
           PERFORM 7000-LOAD-OUTPUT-FILE.                                       
                                                                                
P11295     IF  PV-CRP-LST-RVD-DT >= PV-M1EFF-DT-M30-FMT8                        
P11295     AND PV-CRP-LST-RVD-DT <= PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-X                          
P11295     AND PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT >= PV-M1EFF-DT-M30-FMT8                        
P11295     AND PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT <= PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-X                          
           AND SKSTOO-PO-NBR   > 0                                              
               MOVE SPACES                  TO PV-REP-DONT-SHIP-BEF-DT          
                                               PV-REP-EXPT-DATE                 
               MOVE ZEROES                  TO PV-REP-PO-NBR                    
               MOVE PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT       TO PV-REP-LST-RCVD-DT-SR            
               MOVE '/'                     TO PV-REP-FILLER3                   
                                               PV-REP-FILLER4                   
               MOVE PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT(3:2)  TO PV-REP-CORPDT-YY                 
               MOVE PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT(5:2)  TO PV-REP-CORPDT-MM                 
               MOVE PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT(7:2)  TO PV-REP-CORPDT-DD                 
               MOVE 'REASON1'               TO PV-REP-REASON                    
               PERFORM 8000-WRITE-VALID-FILE                                    
           ELSE                                                                 
               IF  PV-EXPT-DATE-NUM >= PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-NUM                     
               AND PV-EXPT-DATE-NUM <= PV-M1-EFF-DTE30-NUM                      
               AND SKSTOO-PO-NBR   > 0                                          
                   MOVE 'REASON2'           TO PV-REP-REASON                    
                   MOVE SKSTOO-PO-NBR       TO PV-REP-PO-NBR                    
                   MOVE '/'                 TO PV-REP-FILLER1                   
                                               PV-REP-FILLER2                   
                   MOVE PLNSHP-DONT-SHIP-BEF-DTE(3:2)                           
                                            TO PV-REP-POSHIP-YY                 
                   MOVE PLNSHP-DONT-SHIP-BEF-DTE(6:2)                           
                                            TO PV-REP-POSHIP-MM                 
                   MOVE PLNSHP-DONT-SHIP-BEF-DTE(9:2)                           
                                            TO PV-REP-POSHIP-DD                 
                                                                                
                   MOVE '/'                 TO PV-REP-FILLER5                   
                                               PV-REP-FILLER6                   
                   MOVE PV-EXPT-RCT-DT(3:2) TO PV-REP-EXPTDT-YY                 
                   MOVE PV-EXPT-RCT-DT(6:2) TO PV-REP-EXPTDT-MM                 
                   MOVE PV-EXPT-RCT-DT(9:2) TO PV-REP-EXPTDT-DD                 
                   MOVE PV-EXPT-DATE-NUM    TO PV-REP-EXPT-DT-NUM               
                                                                                
                   IF  PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT NOT = ZEROES                           
                       MOVE '/'             TO PV-REP-FILLER3                   
                                               PV-REP-FILLER4                   
                       MOVE PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT(3:2)                              
                                            TO PV-REP-CORPDT-YY                 
                       MOVE PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT(5:2)                              
                                            TO PV-REP-CORPDT-MM                 
                       MOVE PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT(7:2)                              
                                            TO PV-REP-CORPDT-DD                 
                   ELSE                                                         
                       MOVE SPACES          TO PV-REP-LAST-RCVD-DT              
                   END-IF                                                       
                   MOVE PV-STR-LST-RVD-DT   TO PV-REP-LST-RCVD-DT-SR            
                   PERFORM 8000-WRITE-VALID-FILE                                
               END-IF                                                           
           END-IF.                                                              
                                                                                
      ******************************************************************        
      * Description     : Read Mark 1 SKU file                        *         
      ******************************************************************        
       2000-READ-MARK1-SKU-CE1.                                                 
                                                                                
           MOVE '*2000-READ-MARK1-SKU-CE1'  TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME.               
                                                                                
           READ PERM-MARK1-SKU-CE1        INTO PV-MARK1-FILE                    
             AT END SET EOF-MARK1-FILE      TO TRUE                             
           END-READ.                                                            
                                                                                
           IF  NOT-EOF-MARK1-FILE                                               
               ADD 1                        TO PV-INP-RECS-CNT                  
           END-IF.                                                              
                                                                                
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------        
      * LOAD The Mark1 CE1 Report file                                          
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------        
       7000-LOAD-OUTPUT-FILE.                                                   
                                                                                
           MOVE "*7000-LOAD-OUTPUT-FILE*"   TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME                
                                                                                
           MOVE PV-BYR-NBR                  TO PV-REP-BYR-NBR                   
           MOVE PV-DEPT-NBR                 TO PV-REP-DEPT-NBR                  
           MOVE PV-DEPT-NM                  TO PV-REP-DEPT-NM                   
           MOVE PV-SUB-CL-NBR               TO PV-REP-SUB-CL-NBR                
           MOVE PV-VS-NBR                   TO PV-REP-VS-NBR                    
           MOVE PV-SKU-NBR                  TO PV-REP-SKU-NBR                   
           MOVE PV-SKU-STAT-CDE             TO PV-REP-SKU-STAT-CDE              
           MOVE PV-SKU-DESC                 TO PV-REP-SKU-DESC                  
           MOVE PV-CSTM-CLOR-DESC           TO PV-REP-CSTM-CLOR-DESC            
           MOVE PV-PRCHG-ID                 TO PV-REP-PRCHG-ID                  
           MOVE PV-ALL-RMNG-STR-IND         TO PV-REP-ALL-RMNG-IND              
           MOVE 'CE1'                       TO PV-REP-REASON-CODE.              
                                                                                
           IF  PV-EFF-DTE NOT = SPACES                                          
               MOVE '/'                     TO PV-REP-FILLER7                   
                                               PV-REP-FILLER8                   
               MOVE PV-EFF-DTE(3:2)         TO PV-REP-EFF-DT-YER                
               MOVE PV-EFF-DTE(6:2)         TO PV-REP-EFF-DT-MM                 
               MOVE PV-EFF-DTE(9:2)         TO PV-REP-EFF-DT-DD                 
           ELSE                                                                 
               MOVE SPACES                  TO PV-REP-EFF-DTE                   
           END-IF                                                               
                                                                                
                                                                                
           STRING PV-FRST-NM      DELIMITED BY SPACE                            
                  ' '             DELIMITED BY SIZE                             
                  PV-LAST-NM      DELIMITED BY SPACE                            
                                          INTO PV-REP-BYR-NM.                   
                                                                                
P11295 7100-GET-MARK1-MIN30DAYS.                                                
P11295*****************************************************************         
P11295* Description     : To get mark1 eff date minus 30 days     *             
P11295*****************************************************************         
P11295                                                                          
P11295     PERFORM  WITH TEST AFTER                                             
P11295             UNTIL SQLCODE = +0                                           
P11295                OR SQLCODE = +100                                         
P11295                OR PV-RETRY-COUNT > PC-MAXIMUM-RETRY-COUNT                
P11295         EXEC SQL                                                         
P11295             SELECT (DATE(:PV-EFF-DTE) - :PV-DATE-GAP DAYS)               
P11295               INTO :PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-MIN30                               
P11295               FROM  SYSIBM.SYSDUMMY1                                     
P11295             WITH UR                                                      
P11295         END-EXEC                                                         
P11295                                                                          
P11295         EVALUATE TRUE                                                    
P11295             WHEN SQLCODE = ZERO                                          
P11295                 MOVE PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-MIN30(1:4)  TO                     
P11295                      PV-M1EFF-DT-M30-FMT8(1:4)                           
P11295                 MOVE PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-MIN30(6:2)  TO                     
P11295                      PV-M1EFF-DT-M30-FMT8(5:2)                           
P11295                 MOVE PV-MARK1-EFF-DTE-MIN30(9:2)  TO                     
P11295                      PV-M1EFF-DT-M30-FMT8(7:2)                           
P11295             WHEN SQLCODE = -911                                          
P11295             WHEN SQLCODE = -913                                          
P11295                  ADD 1                 TO PV-RETRY-COUNT                 
P11295             WHEN OTHER                                                   
P11295                 MOVE '7100-GET-MARK1-MIN30DAYS'                          
P11295                                        TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME              
P11295                 MOVE 'GET-MARK1-MIN30DAYS'                               
P11295                                        TO PV-DB2-OPER-ATTEMPTED          
P11295                 PERFORM 9999-SQL-ERROR                                   
P11295         END-EVALUATE                                                     
P11295     END-PERFORM.                                                         
P11295                                                                          
P11295     IF  PV-RETRY-COUNT > PC-MAXIMUM-RETRY-COUNT                          
P11295         MOVE '7100-GET-MARK1-MIN30DAYS' TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME             
P11295         MOVE 'GET-MARK1-MIN30DAYS'    TO PV-DB2-OPER-ATTEMPTED           
P11295         PERFORM 9999-SQL-ERROR                                           
P11295     END-IF.                                                              
P11295                                                                          
P11295                                                                          
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------        
      * WRITE The Mark1 CE1 Report file                                         
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------        
       8000-WRITE-VALID-FILE.                                                   
                                                                                
           MOVE "*8000-WRITE-VALID-FILE*"   TO PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME                
                                                                                
           WRITE PERM-RPT-OUTFILE-REC     FROM PV-REP-MARK1-FILE                
                                                                                
           ADD +1                           TO PV-RECS-CNT.                     
                                                                                
                                                                                
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------        
      * 9000-TERMINATE - CLOSES THE FILES ASSOCIATED WITH THE JOB.              
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------        
       9000-TERMINATE.                                                          
                                                                                
           DISPLAY ' '.                                                         
           DISPLAY '============================================='.             
           DISPLAY ' '.                                                         
           DISPLAY ' ******  PEKRP092 PROCESSING SUMMARY  ******  '.            
           PERFORM 9100-DISPLAY-PROCESSING-INFO.                                
           DISPLAY '============================================='.             
                                                                                
           CLOSE                               PERM-MARK1-SKU-CE1               
                                               PERM-RPT-OUTFILE.                
                                                                                
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------        
      * DISPLAY PROCESSED RECORDS COUNTS                                        
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------        
       9100-DISPLAY-PROCESSING-INFO.                                            
                                                                                
            DISPLAY ' '.                                                        
            DISPLAY ' INPUT RECORD COUNT     = ' PV-INP-RECS-CNT                
                                                                                
            DISPLAY ' COUNT OF RECS REPORTED = ' PV-RECS-CNT                    
            DISPLAY ' '.                                                        
                                                                                
      *****************************************************************         
      * 9200-ABEND.                                                   *         
      *  - PERFORM AN ABEND THAT OCCURED RELATED TO FILE              *         
      *****************************************************************         
       9200-ABEND.                                                              
                                                                                
           DISPLAY '** ABEND           **'.                                     
           DISPLAY '** PROGRAM         ** = ' PC-PGM-NAME.                      
           DISPLAY '** PARAGRAPH       ** = ' PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME.                
           DISPLAY '** OPERATION       ** = ' PV-OPERATION-MSG-1.               
           DISPLAY '**                 ** = ' PV-OPERATION-MSG-2.               
                                                                                
           CALL 'ILBOABN0' USING ABEND-CODE.                                    
                                                                                
                                                                                
       9999-SQL-ERROR.                                                          
      ******************************************************************        
      * SQL abend routine                                                       
      ******************************************************************        
                                                                                
           SET ABEND-4013                     TO TRUE.                          
                                                                                
           DISPLAY '**  ABEND     **'.                                          
                                                                                
           DISPLAY '**  PROGRAM   **  =  PEKRP092'.                             
           DISPLAY '**  PARAGRAPH **  = ' PV-PARAGRAPH-NAME.                    
           DISPLAY '**  OPERATION **  = ' PV-DB2-OPER-ATTEMPTED.                
      *                                                                         
      * The following copybook utilizes the DB2 abend module                    
      * DSNTIAR to convert SQLCA into understandable verbage.                   
      *                                                                         
           COPY DPPD004.                                                        
      *                                                                         
                                                                                
           EXEC SQL                                                             
                COMMIT                                                          
           END-EXEC.                                                            
                                                                                
           CALL 'ILBOABN0'  USING ABEND-CODE.                                   
